{"tid":2261310,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"[kickstarter 撚請入］請問比左錢之後係點？","createTime":"2020-10-28T08:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T09:00:27.000Z","uid":294423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"25c13c7d1b67fac291d96eae47519a5238cb0a04","tid":2261310,"uid":294423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:16:08.000Z","msg":"身為一個中坑廢老，第一次用Kickstarter，見到有香港design，諗住支持下，想問比左錢後，如果佢成功籌夠旗，咁我係咪到果個時間就會收到件貨？（佢個schedule 寫2021年8月）<br />\n<br />\n如果籌唔夠旗，咁我比左既錢係會自動退返落去信用卡定係我要同發起人追退款？<br />\n<br />\n咁又如果籌夠旗但出唔到貨，又應該要點做？<br />\n<br />\n平時會特登行下香港設計既舖，但Kickstarter 真係未試過又好似好多得意既野。我好支持將概念實際化既行動，咁社會先會進步。<br />\n<br />\n個香港design 既link: <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/907755211/3d-crystal-puzzle-neuschwanstein-castle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2F907755211%2F3d-crystal-puzzle-neuschwanstein-castle&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7KC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=531d0598\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/907755211/3d-crystal-puzzle-neuschwanstein-castle</a>"},{"pid":"0d926a30a777e80daa55bc07cab8f8ceb2f9494a","tid":2261310,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:19:42.000Z","msg":"得一個字：等"},{"pid":"a630cd7be89dc5ebb1072bafc17e8ed7cda03bc2","tid":2261310,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"算啦，當跌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6674394bd88df948f721ec85264d860661e1dd5","tid":2261310,"uid":21121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"等"},{"pid":"422e4eb4d90079ba32d005084369cf56eed1eddf","tid":2261310,"uid":294423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d926a30a777e80daa55bc07cab8f8ceb2f9494a","tid":2261310,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:19:42.000Z","msg":"得一個字：等"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T0